<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT30">
<l>avaṉeṉṉai yāḷi yaraṅkat taraṅki</l>
<l>lavaṉeṉṉai yeytāmaṟ kāppā ṉavaṉeṉṉa</l>
<l>tuḷḷattu niṉṟā ṉiruntāṉ kiṭakkumē</l>
<l>veḷḷat taravaṇaiyiṉ mēl.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[The Lord] of Raṅgam is the one who rules me.</l>
<l>He guards me against reaching the stage [of the world].</l>
<l>He stood [and] sat in my heart.</l>
<l>Will [He then] recline on the serpent-bed upon the sea?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
